            <p class="text-regular hidden desktop:block desktop:absolute desktop:top-[9.75rem] desktop:left-[29.8125rem] desktop:max-w-[53.35rem]">Dodo IS, our own cloud-based tech platform covers everything from ordering to delivery, production and data-driven multiple-store management.</p>
            <p class="text-regular mobile:hidden desktop:hidden tablet:absolute tablet:top-[12.875rem] tablet:left-[20.25rem] tablet:max-w-[31.875rem]">Dodo IS, our own cloud-based tech platform covers everything from ordering to delivery, production and data-driven multiple-store management.</p>
